100 kim tu Ezechielam pathasva, yaḥ teṣāṃ varṇanam karoti 101 yathā sa teṣāṃ darśanam śīta-diśi cakāra 102 vāyunā saha megheṇa saha ca agninā saha āgacchatām;
103 ye ca teṣāṃ varṇāḥ tasya granthaputreṣu bhavanti, 104 tādṛśāḥ tatra āsann, anyathā pakṣānām viṣaye, 105 yaḥ saṃyogasya viṣaye mama saha Johannas tiṣṭhati, tasmāt sa viyuktaḥ asti.

